data.description: YOU WOULDN'T BELIEVE THE SPACE THIS RANCH BOASTS, COME TAKE A LOOK! This one of a kind home, complete with a full finished basement located in the Highly Sought after Summergrove Community, is a dream come true. As we enter the home, you are welcomed by a large open floor plan that is brought to life by the natural light coming from the large windows that span from the living room to the breakfast nook. To your left, you have your formal dining area, which is large enough to sit 12. To your left, you are welcomed by a large sitting room. With the open kitchen floor plan, you can move freely about, and not to mention it has a view to the living area. The laundry room is located right off the Kitchen in its separate room that has tons of storage space included. The Owners Suite is located on the main level. The oversized room comes with a TV already mounted for your viewing pleasure. Enjoy your privacy with your personal En Suite that includes a standup shower and a Garden Tub, Double Vanity sinks, and a large walk-in closet with custom shelving systems included. On the other side of the main level are 2 full-size bedrooms, sharing a bathroom as well as a flex room with built-in cabinetry and desks, this can double as a great play/study room for the kids. Upstairs you will find an OVERSIZED bedroom with its private bathroom. Large enough to have a living and sleeping area, the possibilities are truly endless in this space. Let's head downstairs to the fully finished basement which is the hidden gem of the home. This space is HUGE! Let's start with the theater room, equipped with 7.1 Definitive Technology Surround powered by a Yamaha Receiver, Projector, and Projector Screen this is a Movie Lover's dream! Full Kitchen located in the basement with a pantry the size of a walk-in closet. The kitchen overlooks the downstairs living room area, also equipped with surround sound. You'll also find a built-in 2-person office, Gym, Full Bathroom equipped with a State of the Art toilet as well as a walk-in closet, Full bedroom with a walk-in closet that also leads to a walk-in storage area. The HVAC is one year old, the home has a tankless water heater, Osmosis filtering & purifying drinking water, and a water softener system. Outside of the tons of space you get in this home, you have the greatest perk of being situated on the 17th hole of the Golf Course. Talk about living on the Green. The community comes with great amenities such as Playgrounds, Tennis Courts, Pickleball courts, 3 Swimming Pools, a Lazy River, a LINC Trail, and a Beautiful lake for Kayaking and fishing. Come see your dream home conveniently located close to shopping, I-85, Hartsfield-Jackson Airport, Peachtree City and so many other surrounding places. WHAT MORE CAN YOU ASK FOR?
